data.title: Faculty and Staff Directory
data.text: Clicking the button below constitutes your express written consent, without obligation to purchase, to be contacted by Vaughn College (including through automated technology, e.g. dialing and text messaging) via the telephone or mobile device (including SMS and MMS) using the phone numbers provided above, and/or email, even if your telephone number is on a corporate, state or the National Do Not Call Registry, and you agree to our terms of use and privacy policy. Standard message and data rates apply.
